<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_45_r1l14">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / VVir bıten ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ / daʒ ewr gnade </ab>
